==Introduction==
遠距離砲撃戦における秘密兵器「九一式徹甲弾」の改良版です。<br>
海中突入後魚雷のように敵艦水線下に突き進み、喫水下破砕を企図した特殊徹甲弾です。<br>
九一式より性能・生産性が向上しており、弾頭部には弾着観測用着色剤を充填していたと云われています。<br>
戦艦・航空戦艦・高速戦艦で使用可能です。 

''The Type 1 Armor Piercing shell is an improved version of the secret Type 91 Armor Piercing shell fired from long range cannons.'' <br>
''It is intended to work by plunging into the sea, striking the hull below the waterline of the enemy ship like a torpedo.'' <br>
''It has better performance than they Type 91, and has colored dyes for identification and target assists.'' <br>
''It can be equipped on battleships, aviation battleships and fast battleships.''

==Notes==
'''Unbuildable'''. Quest reward from [[Quests#B31|B31]] and [[Quests#B32|B32]], can be gained through [[Akashi's Improvement Arsenal]]. <br>Reward for completing seasonal [[Seasonal/New_Year_2016#Quests|quest SB10]] during New Year's 2016.

